      "title": "A special rehearsal in Parliament tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A special rehearsal of the opening ceremony of the Parliament will be held tomorrow, said Mr. Vetradhari Narendra Fernando.",
        "Parliament, which has ended its term, is scheduled to be ceremonially opened by President Ranil Wickramasinghe on Wednesday (3rd)."
